    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">ZAP Command</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><snippet src="__CommandInclude" inline="false"/></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Heading1">Purpose</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">Permanently remove all records from database file in the current work area.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Heading1">Syntax</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">ZAP &#160;[[IN|ALIAS] workarea] </para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Heading1">Arguments</text></para>
    <para styleclass="List"></para>
    <para styleclass="List"><snippet src="__In" inline="false"/></para>
    <para styleclass="List"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Heading1">Description</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">ZAP is functionally equivalent to <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="html\M_XSharp_RT_Functions_DbZap.htm" domain="XsRuntime.chm">DBZap()</link>. &#160;</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
